Capital Markets

Company Overview of Global Macro Trust



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Global Macro Trust engages in trading futures, forwards, spot currency contracts, options, and swap contracts. It trades in the agricultural, metals, energy, interest rate, and stock indices futures markets, as well as in the currency markets and trading primarily forward contracts in the interbank market. The company was founded in 2001 and is based in Greenwich, Connecticut.


411 West Putnam AvenueGreenwich, CT 06830United StatesFounded in 2001



Phone: 203-625-7554








