Welcome to Global Macro Investor
The Global Macro Investor is an internationally-renowned and highly successful  monthly global macro advisory publication with occasional intra-monthly updates for time-critical analysis or recommendations. It is read by many of the world's largest and most successful hedge funds, pension funds, sovereign wealth funds and family offices. However, it is not aimed at individual investors due to the complexities of the subject matter and risks involved.
The service covers all aspects of global macro investing, from taking advantage of secular trends to shorter-term opportunities, and covers all asset classes (FX, Fixed Income, Equities and Commodities). The product features in-depth analysis of economies and asset classes, along with specific and actionable trade recommendations. It utilises both fundamental and technical analysis in conjunction with the business cycle in order to optimse the risk rewards of the trading opportunities.






